        <abstract> 
<p>Accepts JM’s terms for publication of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. If, on reading the MS, JM thinks it will not sell, CD frees him from the offer. Will send chapters soon so he can judge. Though some parts are dry and abstruse, CD thinks it will be interesting to "those who care for the curious problem of the origin of all animate forms".</p> 
        </abstract>
